Uniform Model¶

In [3]:
%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Uniform model

# parameters & statistics
a.uni <- 0
b.uni <- 4
mu.uni <- a.uni+b.uni/2
sigma.uni <- sqrt((b.uni-a.uni)^2/12)
  
# plot
range.uni <- seq(from=a.uni, to=b.uni, by=0.01)
y1.uni <- runif(n=length(range.uni), min=a.uni, max=b.uni)
y2.uni <- dunif(x=range.uni, min=a.uni, max=b.uni)
y3.uni <- punif(q=range.uni, min=a.uni, max=b.uni)

rplt.uni <- ggplot(tibble(range.uni, y1.uni), aes(x=y1.uni, y=range.uni)) +
  geom_point(size=0.5) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-0.5, 4.5)) +
  labs(title='Uniform Distribution, a=0, b=4', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.uni, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.uni-sigma.uni, xmax=mu.uni+sigma.uni,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.uni <- ggplot(tibble(range.uni, y2.uni), aes(x=range.uni, y=y2.uni)) +
  geom_density() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.uni, size=0.2) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-0.5, 4.5), ylim=c(0, 0.4)) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.uni-sigma.uni, xmax=mu.uni+sigma.uni,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.uni <- ggplot(tibble(range.uni, y3.uni), aes(x=range.uni, y=y3.uni)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.uni, size=0.2) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-0.5, 4.5), ylim=c(0, 1)) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.uni-sigma.uni, xmax=mu.uni+sigma.uni,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 

plot_grid(rplt.uni, dplt.uni, pplt.uni, nrow=3,
          labels=c('runif()', 'dunif()', 'punif()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Standard Normal model

# parameters & statistics
mu.nrm <- 0
sigma.nrm <- 1

# plot
range.nrm <- seq(from=mu.nrm-4*sigma.nrm, to=mu.nrm+4*sigma.nrm, by=0.01)
y1.nrm <- rnorm(n=length(range.nrm), mean=mu.nrm, sd=sigma.nrm)
y2.nrm <- dnorm(x=range.nrm, mean=mu.nrm, sd=sigma.nrm)
y3.nrm <- pnorm(q=range.nrm, mean=mu.nrm, sd=sigma.nrm)

rplt.nrm <- ggplot(tibble(range.nrm, y1.nrm), aes(x=y1.nrm, y=range.nrm)) +
  geom_point(size=0.3) + 
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-4, 4)) +
  labs(title='Standard Normal Distribution, mu=0, sigma=1', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.nrm, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.nrm-sigma.nrm, xmax=mu.nrm+sigma.nrm,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.nrm <- ggplot(tibble(range.nrm, y2.nrm), aes(x=range.nrm, y=y2.nrm)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.nrm, size=0.2) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-4, 4)) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.nrm-sigma.nrm, xmax=mu.nrm+sigma.nrm,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.nrm <- ggplot(tibble(range.nrm, y3.nrm), aes(x=range.nrm, y=y3.nrm)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.nrm, size=0.2) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim=c(-4, 4)) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.nrm-sigma.nrm, xmax=mu.nrm+sigma.nrm,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 

plot_grid(rplt.nrm, dplt.nrm, pplt.nrm, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rnorm()', 'dnorm()', 'pnorm()'))

Exponential Model¶

In [5]:
%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Exponential model

# parameters & statistics
lambda.exp <- 1/2.725
mu.exp <- 1/lambda.exp
sigma.exp <- sqrt(1/lambda.exp^2)

# plot
range.exp <- seq(from=0, to=mu.exp+5*sigma.exp, by=0.01)
y1.exp <- rexp(n=length(range.exp), rate=lambda.exp)
y2.exp <- dexp(x=range.exp, rate=lambda.exp)
y3.exp <- pexp(q=range.exp, rate=lambda.exp)

rplt.exp <- ggplot(tibble(range.exp, y1.exp), aes(x=y1.exp, y=range.exp)) +
  geom_point(size=0.2) + 
  labs(title='Exponential Distribution, lambda=1/2.725', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.exp, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.exp-sigma.exp, xmax=mu.exp+sigma.exp,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.exp <- ggplot(tibble(range.exp, y2.exp), aes(x=range.exp, y=y2.exp)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.exp, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.exp-sigma.exp, xmax=mu.exp+sigma.exp,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.exp <- ggplot(tibble(range.exp, y3.exp), aes(x=range.exp, y=y3.exp)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.exp, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.exp-sigma.exp, xmax=mu.exp+sigma.exp,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
    
plot_grid(rplt.exp, dplt.exp, pplt.exp, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rexp()', 'dexp()', 'pexp()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Gamma model

# parameters & statistics
alpha.gam <- 5
beta.gam <- 12.4
lambda.gam <- 1/beta.gam^2
mu.gam <- alpha.gam*beta.gam
sigma.gam <- sqrt(alpha.gam/(1/beta.gam)^2) # alt <- sqrt(alpha.gam*beta.gam^2)

# plot
range.gam <- seq(from=0, to=mu.gam+5*sigma.gam, by=0.05)
y1.gam <- rgamma(n=length(range.gam), shape=alpha.gam, rate=1/beta.gam)
y2.gam <- dgamma(x=range.gam, shape=alpha.gam, rate=1/beta.gam)
y3.gam <- pgamma(q=range.gam, shape=alpha.gam, rate=1/beta.gam)

rplt.gam <- ggplot(tibble(range.gam, y1.gam), aes(x=y1.gam, y=range.gam)) +
  geom_point(size=0.1) + 
  labs(title='Gamma Distribution, alpha=5, beta=12.4', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.gam, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.gam-sigma.gam, xmax=mu.gam+sigma.gam,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.gam <- ggplot(tibble(range.gam, y2.gam), aes(x=range.gam, y=y2.gam)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.gam, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.gam-sigma.gam, xmax=mu.gam+sigma.gam,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.gam <- ggplot(tibble(range.gam, y3.gam), aes(x=range.gam, y=y3.gam)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.gam, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.gam-sigma.gam, xmax=mu.gam+sigma.gam,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 

plot_grid(rplt.gam, dplt.gam, pplt.gam, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rgamma()', 'dgamma()', 'pgamma()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Chi-squared model

# parameters & statistics
k.chi <- 7
mu.chi <- k.chi
sigma.chi <- sqrt(2*k.chi)

# plot

y1.chi <- rchisq(n=length(range.chi), df=k.chi)

y3.chi <- pchisq(q=range.chi, df=k.chi)

rplt.chi <- ggplot(tibble(range.chi, y1.chi), aes(x=y1.chi, y=range.chi)) +
  geom_point(size=0.1) + 
  labs(title='Chi-Square Distribution, k=7', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.chi, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.chi-sigma.chi, xmax=mu.chi+sigma.chi,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.chi <- ggplot(tibble(range.chi, y2.chi), aes(x=range.chi, y=y2.chi)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.chi, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.chi-sigma.chi, xmax=mu.chi+sigma.chi,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.chi <- ggplot(tibble(range.chi, y3.chi), aes(x=range.chi, y=y3.chi)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.chi, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.chi-sigma.chi, xmax=mu.chi+sigma.chi,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
    
plot_grid(rplt.chi, dplt.chi, pplt.chi, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rchisq()', 'dchisq()', 'pchisq()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Beta model

# parameters & statistics
alpha.bet <- 6
beta.bet <- 2
mu.bet <- alpha.bet/(alpha.bet+beta.bet)
sigma.bet <- sqrt((alpha.bet*beta.bet)/
                  ((alpha.bet+beta.bet)^2*(alpha.bet+beta.bet+1))) 

# plot
range.bet <- seq(from=0, to=mu.bet+5*sigma.bet, by=0.001)
y1.bet <- rbeta(n=length(range.bet), shape1=alpha.bet, shape2=beta.bet)
y2.bet <- dbeta(x=range.bet, shape1=alpha.bet, shape2=beta.bet)
y3.bet <- pbeta(q=range.bet, shape1=alpha.bet, shape2=beta.bet)

rplt.bet <- ggplot(tibble(range.bet, y1.bet), aes(x=y1.bet, y=range.bet)) +
  geom_point(size=0.1) + 
  labs(title='Beta Distribution, alpha=6, beta=2', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.bet, size=0.2) +
  xlim(0, 1) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.bet-sigma.bet, xmax=mu.bet+sigma.bet,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
dplt.bet <- ggplot(tibble(range.bet, y2.bet), aes(x=range.bet, y=y2.bet)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.bet, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  xlim(0, 1) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.bet-sigma.bet, xmax=mu.bet+sigma.bet,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.bet <- ggplot(tibble(range.bet, y3.bet), aes(x=range.bet, y=y3.bet)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.bet, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  xlim(0, 1) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.bet-sigma.bet, xmax=mu.bet+sigma.bet,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 

plot_grid(rplt.bet, dplt.bet, pplt.bet, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rbeta()', 'dbeta()', 'pbeta()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## Students t model

# parameters & statistics
k.t <- 7
a.t <- 1.5
mu.t <- a.t
sigma.t <- sqrt((k.t-1)/(k.t-1-2))

# plot
range.t <- seq(from=mu.t-5*sigma.t, to=mu.t+5*sigma.t, by=0.005)
y1.t <- rt(n=length(range.t), df=k.t-1, ncp=a.t)
y2.t <- dt(x=range.t, df=k.t-1, ncp=a.t)
y3.t <- pt(q=range.t, df=k.t-1, ncp=a.t)

rplt.t <- ggplot(tibble(range.t, y1.t), aes(x=y1.t, y=range.t)) +
  geom_point(size=0.1) + 
  labs(title='Student\'s-t Distribution, k=7, a=1.5', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.t, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.t-sigma.t, xmax=mu.t+sigma.t,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1)
dplt.t <- ggplot(tibble(range.t, y2.t), aes(x=range.t, y=y2.t)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.t, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.t-sigma.t, xmax=mu.t+sigma.t,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 
pplt.t <- ggplot(tibble(range.t, y3.t), aes(x=range.t, y=y3.t)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.t, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.t-sigma.t, xmax=mu.t+sigma.t,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1) 

plot_grid(rplt.t, dplt.t, pplt.t, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rt()', 'dt()', 'pt()'))

%%R -w 5 -h 8 --units in -r 200
## F model

# parameters & statistics
k1.F <- 16
k2.F <- 7
mu.F <- (k2.F-1)/((k2.F-1)-2)
sigma.F <- sqrt((2*(k2.F-1)^2)*(k1.F+k2.F-4)/((k1.F-1)*(k2.F-3))^2*(k2.F-5))

# plot
range.F <- seq(from=0, to=mu.F+5*sigma.F, by=0.005)
y1.F <- rf(n=length(range.F), df1=k1.F, df2=k2.F)
y2.F <- df(x=range.F, df1=k1.F, df2=k2.F)
y3.F <- pf(q=range.F, df1=k1.F, df2=k2.F)

rplt.F <- ggplot(tibble(range.F, y1.F), aes(x=y1.F, y=range.F)) +
  geom_point(size=0.1) + 
  labs(title='F Distribution, k1=16, k2=7', x=NULL, y='value') +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.F, size=0.2) +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.F-sigma.F, xmax=mu.F+sigma.F,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1)
dplt.F <- ggplot(tibble(range.F, y2.F), aes(x=range.F, y=y2.F)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.F, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x=NULL, y='f(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.F-sigma.F, xmax=mu.F+sigma.F,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1)
pplt.F <- ggplot(tibble(range.F, y3.F), aes(x=range.F, y=y3.F)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_vline(xintercept=mu.F, size=0.2) +
  labs(title='', x='range', y='F(x)') +
  annotate('rect', xmin=mu.F-sigma.F, xmax=mu.F+sigma.F,
           ymin=-Inf, ymax=Inf, alpha=0.1)

plot_grid(rplt.F, dplt.F, pplt.F, nrow=3,
          labels=c('rf()', 'df()', 'pf()'))
